OL,3,CExtra security at Rob Burrow MND
OL,4,Ccentre after thefts
OL,6,FCraige Richardson, Director of Estates
OL,7,Fand Facilities at Leeds Teaching
OL,8,FHospitals, said: "We are working with
OL,9,FWest Yorkshire Police, and we have
OL,10,Falso put in place extra security
OL,11,Fmeasures at the site.
OL,13,F"We will always take positive action
OL,14,Fagainst criminal activity at our
OL,15,Fhospitals, including prosecution.
OL,17,F"The new state-of-the-art Centre will
OL,18,Fprovide a calm and peaceful
OL,19,Fenvironment for patients living with
OL,20,FMND and their families. We remain on
OL,21,Ftrack to open in summer 2025."
