OL,3,CExtra security at Rob Burrow MND
OL,4,Ccentre after thefts
OL,6,FIt is unclear when the thefts took
OL,7,Fplace and what was taken from the site.
OL,9,F#6.8million was fundraised to create
OL,10,Fthe flagship centre to care for MND
OL,11,Fpatients in honour of Rob Burrow who
OL,12,Fhad the disease.
OL,14,FConstruction work started in June
OL,15,Fshortly after the former player's
OL,16,Fdeath at the age of 41. It is due to
OL,17,Fbe completed this summer.
OL,19,FITV News has contacted West Yorkshire
OL,20,FPolice for comment.
